Package com.intellij.refactoring.inline

Class InlineObjectProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.refactoring.BaseRefactoringProcessor
      • com.intellij.refactoring.inline.InlineObjectProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class InlineObjectProcessor
extends BaseRefactoringProcessor
    Performs inlining of object construction together with a subsequent call. E.g. new Point(12, 34).getX() could be inlined to 12.
